{"tid":2181984,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「黑豹」Chadwick Boseman 死訊　成 Twitter 史上 Like 數最高帖","createTime":"2020-08-31T04:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T20:36:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e34af6e3198a6c0dbd91a2207fec56295700d3cd","tid":2181984,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:17:43.000Z","msg":"Marvel 超級英雄電影《黑豹 (Black Panther)》男主角 Chadwick Boseman 當地時間昨日（28 日）因大腸癌去世，年僅 43 歲。全球大批網民在網上致哀。其&nbsp;Twitter 發布的死訊帖文，至今已有超過 720 萬「Like」。據 CNN 報道，該帖文成為 Twitter 史上最高「Like」的一則消息。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Twitter Like 數排名第二的，是奧巴馬於 2017 年分享的一則帖文，該帖有超過 430 萬 likes。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%93%80%E6%82%BC-%E9%BB%91%E8%B1%B9-chadwick-boseman-%E6%AD%BB%E8%A8%8A-%E6%88%90-twitter-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A-like-%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2593%2580%25E6%2582%25BC-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25B1%25B9-chadwick-boseman-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%2588%2590-twitter-%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A-like-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B8%2596%2F&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoE9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=0d69c442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2593%2580%25E6%2582%25BC-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25B1%25B9-chadwick-boseman-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%2588%2590-twitter-%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A-like-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B8%2596%2F&h=714c9c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%93%80%E6%82%BC-%E9%BB%91%E8%B1%B9-chadwick-boseman-%E6%AD%BB%E8%A8%8A-%E6%88%90-twitter-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A-like-%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%96/</a>"},{"pid":"173c432c5283d33c24f5b39530dfe7555ec7ade1","tid":2181984,"uid":151333,"like":5,"dislike":2